00:57:09,134 --> 00:57:10,343
Apakah mendesak?

709
00:57:10,927 --> 00:57:12,929
Jika kau menemukannya besok siang,

710
00:57:13,555 --> 00:57:15,306
akan kubayar tiga kali lipat.

711
00:57:16,683 --> 00:57:17,725
Baik.

712
